highlights.text: “Lạ Lùng” by Vũ. has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 387 weeks straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #3.
“Nỗi Đau Giữa Hòa Bình” by Hoà Minzy and Nguyen Van Chung is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 115 spots at #32.
“Nhà Tôi Có Treo Một Lá Cờ” by DTAP and Hà Anh Tuấn is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #80.
